# Ignore all font directories except those committed to the repo.
# Fonts like NotoSansCJK are downloaded on demand by build-sd-fonts.py.
*
!.gitignore
!NotoSerif/
!NotoSerif/**
!NotoSans/
!NotoSans/**
!OpenDyslexic/
!OpenDyslexic/**
!Ubuntu/
!Ubuntu/**
# NotoSansSC: keep the helper scripts + license, exclude the heavy OTF
# (fetched on demand via fetch.sh, ~8 MB).
!NotoSansSC/
!NotoSansSC/.gitignore
!NotoSansSC/fetch.sh
!NotoSansSC/OFL.txt
